import { createStore ,combineReducers } from "redux";
import {Addcartdetail} from './reducers'
import {Showlogin} from './reducers'

var login =Showlogin
var reducers = combineReducers({Addcartdetail,Showlogin})
var store = createStore(login)

 export default store
store.dispatch({type:"login"})

 store.dispatch({type:"remove_cart"})
 console.log("store " , store.getState())
 store.dispatch({type:"logout"})
 store.dispatch({type:"Add_Cart"})
 console.log("store " , store.getState())
